<!doctype html>
<html lang="en"
    style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0;margin-left:0;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-right:0;padding-left:0;border-width:0;font-size:inherit;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;font-family:inherit;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline;">

<head>
    <!-- Required meta tags -->
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <title>Verifikasi Email</title>
</head>

<body
    style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0;margin-left:0;padding-top:1px;padding-bottom:0;padding-right:0;padding-left:0;border-width:0;font-size:inherit;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:1;font-family:Bahnschrift, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-weight:normal;background-color:rgb(235,235,235);">
    <div class="atas"
        style="text-align:center;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-right:0;padding-left:0;border-width:0;font-size:inherit;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;font-family:inherit;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline;display:grid;margin-top:25px;margin-bottom:25px;margin-right:0;margin-left:0;">
        <a class="navbar-brand logo1 logo-u" href="#"
            style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0;margin-left:0;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-right:0;padding-left:0;border-width:0;font-size:inherit;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;font-family:inherit;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline-block;justify-self:center;">
            <img src="genbookz.com/img/logo2.png" height="70" class="d-inline-block align-top gmbr-logo" alt="" loading="lazy"
                style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0;margin-left:0;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-right:0;padding-left:0;border-width:0;font-size:inherit;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;font-family:inherit;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline;filter:opacity(0.8);">
            <p class="logo logo-u1"
                style="margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-right:0;padding-left:0;border-width:0;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;vertical-align:baseline;font-family:'Montserrat', sans-serif;font-weight:600;font-size:22pt;display:inline-block;line-height:34px;margin-top:2px;margin-left:-2px;color:#d000cd;">
            </p>
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="form-kotak"
        style="padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-right:0;padding-left:0;border-width:0;font-size:inherit;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;font-family:inherit;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;max-width:585px;">
        <div class="form-daftar"
            style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0;margin-left:0;border-width:0;font-size:inherit;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;font-family:inherit;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline;background-color:white;padding-top:37px;padding-bottom:37px;padding-right:30px;padding-left:30px;border-radius:8px;color:black;">
            <div class="isi"
                style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0;margin-left:0;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-right:0;padding-left:0;border-width:0;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:lighter;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;">
                <div class="judul"
                    style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-left:0;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-right:0;padding-left:0;border-width:0;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-family:inherit;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:20px;font-weight:normal;margin-bottom:15px;">
                    Halo!</div>
                <span
                    style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0;margin-left:0;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-right:0;padding-left:0;border-width:0;font-size:inherit;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:lighter;font-family:inherit;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline;">Ini adalah email untuk memverifikasi akun Genbookz yang kamu daftarkan dengan alamat email ini. Klik tombol di bawah ini untuk verifikasi email kamu.</span>
                <div class="tombol-daftar text-center"
                    style="padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-right:0;padding-left:0;border-width:0;font-size:inherit;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;font-family:inherit;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:25px;margin-bottom:25px;margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-align:center;">
                    <a href="{{$url}}" role="submit" class="btn btn-secondary btn-daftar"
                        style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0;margin-left:0;border-width:0;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline-block;background-color:#ff00ff;border-color:#ff00ff;font-size:15px;line-height:1;padding-top:7px;padding-bottom:5px;padding-right:7px;padding-left:7px;border-radius:8px;width:150px;text-decoration:none;color:white;font-weight:normal;">Verifikasi
                        Email</a>
                </div>
                <span
                    style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0;margin-left:0;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-right:0;padding-left:0;border-width:0;font-size:inherit;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:lighter;font-family:inherit;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline;">Jika kamu tidak membuat akun Genbookz, abaikan email ini dan kamu tidak perlu melakukan apapun.</span>
                <div class="salam"
                    style="margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0;margin-left:0;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-right:0;padding-left:0;border-width:0;font-size:inherit;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:lighter;font-family:inherit;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:15px;">
                    Salam hangat,</div>
                <span
                    style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0;margin-left:0;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-right:0;padding-left:0;border-width:0;font-size:inherit;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:lighter;font-family:inherit;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline;">Genbookz</span>
                <hr>
            </div>

            <div class="link-isi"
                style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0;margin-left:0;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-right:0;padding-left:0;border-width:0;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-family:inherit;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:lighter;font-size:14px;color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);">
                <span
                    style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0;margin-left:0;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-right:0;padding-left:0;border-width:0;font-size:inherit;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:lighter;font-family:inherit;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline;">Jika
                    kamu ada masalah dalam mengklik tombol "Verifikasi email", <em
                        style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0;margin-left:0;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-right:0;padding-left:0;border-width:0;font-size:inherit;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;font-family:inherit;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline;">copy</em>
                    dan <em
                        style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0;margin-left:0;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-right:0;padding-left:0;border-width:0;font-size:inherit;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;font-family:inherit;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline;">paste</em>
                    URL ini ke web browser kamu : {{$url}}</span>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cr text-center"
        style="margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0;margin-left:0;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:25px;padding-right:0;padding-left:0;border-width:0;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;font-family:inherit;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline;text-align:center;margin-top:40px;color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);font-size:12px;">
        &copy;Genbookz 2020. All rights reserved.
    </div>
</body>

</html>